Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 稳住，苏鲁 - 我们还在轨道上，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Stay on top of it, Mr. Sulu. - We're holding orbit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,船舵失灵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The helm is sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,控制电路即将超负荷，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Control circuits threatening to overload, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了，轮机长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Understood, engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们无法躲开这些危险区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we can't avoid these areas of turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再绕几圈轨道，我就能把它们标出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe we'll have them plotted in a few more orbits, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,医务人员，快来舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sickbay, to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,转为人工控制，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Switching to manual, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们还要维持现有轨道吗？ - 史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do we maintain this orbit? - Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，舰长，从科学角度讲这意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is of great scientific importance, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上，我们现在正在穿越时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're actually passing through ripples in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 维持现有轨道 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Maintain orbit. - Aye, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,联系星舰司令部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open a channel to Starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是，长官 - 预防措施，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. - Precautionary measure, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,将上周舰长日志发给司令部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Broadcast to Starfleet Command my past week's log entries,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就从仪表读数异常开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}starting with the unusual readings we had on the instruments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,以及那些数据如何带我们来这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and how they led us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉司令部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inform Starfleet Command that apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗星球上的某种东西或者某个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}something or someone down on this planet--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能让时间产生异变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}--can affect changes in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,造成空间紊乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}causing turbulent waves of space displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,心动过速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some heart flutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看来要冒一下险，给他注射点可酌辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd better risk a few drops of cordrazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这种药不好把握，你确定？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's tricky stuff. Are you sure you wanna risk--?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才想教我行医，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were about to make a medical comment, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谁，我吗，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who, me, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现已避开大部分时空扭曲，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're guiding around most of the time ripples now, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩一块区域未标绘，舰长，就快了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All plotted but one, captain. Coming up on it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这块区域似乎扭曲得很厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seems to be fairly heavy displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,回到各自岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get back to your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是皮下注射器，舰长 - 里面装的是可酌辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The hypo, captain. - It was set for cordrazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 空了 - 通讯官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Empty. - Communications,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫紧急医疗小组\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}emergency medical team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些杀手！刺客！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Killers! Assassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你们得逞！我会先杀了你们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let you! I'll kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你们得逞！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不会得逞的！你们这些杀人犯！杀手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You won't get me! Murderers! Killers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,发出安全警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命和新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}TLF荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：小青龙马\N校对：Nick 喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二十八集\N永恒边境之城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,两滴可酌辛，就能救人一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two drops of cordrazine can save a man's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而麦考伊医生刚刚却意外地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A hundred times that amount
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,接受了一百倍剂量的药物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has just accidentally been pumped into Dr. McCoy's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他发了狂，并逃离了舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and in a strange wild frenzy, he has fled the ship's bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,相邻甲板层都处于警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All connecting decks have been placed on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道他的精神异常会持续多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have no way of knowing if the madness is permanent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也无法确定会给麦考伊带来什么后果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or temporary or in what direction it will drive McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,4号到11号甲板层…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue alert...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…继续保持警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Decks 4 through 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗部知道的情况并不比我们多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Medical department knows as little as we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有记录显示，此剂量的药物可致重度偏执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In dosages approaching this, there's some record of wild paranoia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这与文献库的资料一致，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Confirmed by the library record tapes, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,患者不能辨认熟人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Subjects failed to recognise acquaintances,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,固执地认为自己面临致命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}became hysterically convinced that they were in mortal danger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,并且会拼命逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and were seeking escape at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这种状态很危险，无论对他自己还是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Extremely dangerous to himself or to anyone else who might--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥，这里是安全部，警报，警报 - 这里是舰桥，请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge, Security. Alert, alert. - Bridge here. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是054号安保员，长官，传送部主管受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security 054, sir. We just found the transporter chief injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，麦考伊医生自行登陆了这颗星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, Dr. McCoy has beamed himself down to the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，那时候传送装置的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the transporter at that time, captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正对准着时间扭曲的中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was focused on the centre of the time disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不论那是什么，麦考伊现正位于其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So whatever's down there, McCoy is in the heart of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,组织登陆小队，我们去带他回来，呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Set up a landing party. Let's go get him. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这些废墟一直延伸到地平线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These ruins extend to the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开始记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Begin recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,正在记录，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Recording, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这些废墟的历史相当久远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And of considerable age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,接近一万个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the order of 10,000 centuries old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,分遣队，散开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Detail, fan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is this thing, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎在散发着某种能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seems to be pulsating with power of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,分析一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Analysis, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难以置信，舰长 - 有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Unbelievable, captain. - That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个物体正是时间扭曲的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This single object is the source of all the time displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 解释一下 - 我无法解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Explain. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,基于我所拥有的科学知识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For this to do what it does is impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法对此作出解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by any science I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它仍然在不断发射…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is operating even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…能导致时间扭曲的能量波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...putting out waves and waves of time displacement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在几百万英里外就收到过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which we picked up millions of miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆部队呼叫进取号，没有麦考伊医生的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Landing party to Enterprise. No sign of Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,搜索继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Search progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,惊人的能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Incredible power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能是我们所知的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It can't be a machine as we understand mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那它到底是什么？ - 是一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Then what is it? - A question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们的太阳诞生之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since before your sun burned hot in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们的种族诞生之前，我就在等候一个问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and before your race was born, I have awaited a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是什么？ - 我是永恒的守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are you? - I am the Guardian of Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是机器还是生命？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you machine or being?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都是也都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am both and neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我既是自己的开始，也是自己的结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am my own beginning, my own ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂为什么你要用谜语做答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see no reason for answers to be couched in riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我已尽力简化答案以便你们理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I answer as simply as your level of understanding makes possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一道时间之门，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A time portal, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是一道通向其他时空间的门，如果我没猜错的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A gateway to other times and dimensions, if I'm correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们而言，这种理解已经足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As correct as possible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,显然，你们的科技水平还很原始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your science knowledge is obviously primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，郁闷吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Annoyed, Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们愿意的话，可以通过这里回到过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A gateway to your own past, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些杀手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Killers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你们抓到我的！我要杀了你们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Killers! I won't let you get me! I'll kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你们…你们这些刺客！杀手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let you get-- Assassins! Murderers! Killers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那是可以让我们回到过去的门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If that is a doorway back through time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不可以把老骨头带回一天前，然后…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could we somehow take Bones back a day in time, then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再度经历那次事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Relive the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这次要避免意外发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This time be certain that the hypo accident is avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，门里的时间流逝很快，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at the speed with which the centuries are passing, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要精确地穿越到那一天，恐怕…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To step through on precisely the day we wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你能改变时间流逝的速度吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you change the speed at which yesterday passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我生来就如此，不能改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was made to offer the past in this manner. I cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,越过那扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strangely compelling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,迷失在另外一个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To step through there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪而诱人的想法，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and lose oneself in another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是失策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种速度下我们的三录仪还管用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our tricorder is capable of recording even at this speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我却忘了记录鲜活的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've missed taping centuries of living history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 以前从来没人亲眼… - 麦考伊医生！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- which no man before has ever-- - Dr. McCoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，不要！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他去哪了？ - 他穿越到了过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where is he? - He has passed into what was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我和星舰失去了联系，刚才还在通话中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I've lost contact with the ship. I was talking to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就失灵了，没有静电干扰，没有信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and suddenly, it went dead. No static, just nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯装置没有问题，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing wrong with the communicator, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的星舰，你们的起源，所有的一切都消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your vessel, your beginning, all that you knew is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,…改变了历史的轨迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...has somehow changed history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被困在这了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean we're stranded down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有过去，没有未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With no past, no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我感到害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I'm frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所熟悉的那个地球消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth's not there, at least not the Earth we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在完全孤立无援了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're totally alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历不复存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, no stardate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经无法计算时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For us, time does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,回到了过去的麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy, back somewhere in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,改变了历史进程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has effected a change in the course of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,地球的历史已经改变，进取号也消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All Earth history has been changed. There is no starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们只有一次机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have only one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们请求守卫者再现地球的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have asked the Guardian to show us Earth's history again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克和我将回到过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock and I will go back into time ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试纠正被麦考伊改变的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and attempt to set right whatever it was that McCoy changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊走的时候，我正在记录影像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was recording images at the time McCoy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时期你们美国尚未开化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A rather barbaric period in your American history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以大致判断什么时候进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe I can approximate just when to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,误差可能在一个月之内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps within a month of the correct time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的话一周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a week, if we're fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须在麦考伊之前到达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make sure we arrive before McCoy got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须阻止他…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's vital we stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…在他做出改变整个历史的举动之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...before he does whatever it was that changed all history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,守护者…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guardian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- …如果我们成功了—— - 你们就可以平安归来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...if we are successful-- - Then you will be returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你们从未离开过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will be as though none of you had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这项任务不太可能完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, it seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你们能顺利回到合适的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even if you're able to find the right date--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也不太可能找到麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then even finding McCoy would be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,…如果过了很久我们都没有回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...when you think you've waited long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都要试一试，即使失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}each of you will have to try it. Even if you fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你们也会在过去的某个地方活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at least you'll be alive in some past world somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命 - 只剩下几秒了，长官，准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Aye. - Seconds now, sir. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，祝你们好运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good luck, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,至少要好好地活着，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Happiness at least, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…现在！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过这个时期的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've seen old photographs of this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当时发生了经济危机 - 被称为大萧条时期，大约在1930年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- An economic upheaval had occurred. - It was called Depression, circa 1930.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,相当萧条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的服饰似乎与这个时代不太相称\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We seem to be costumed a little out of step with the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕他们会难以接受我的外表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid I'm going to be difficult to explain in any case, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，史波克，如果无法伪装，那我们要设法…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Mr. Spock, if we can't disguise you, we'll find some way of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 解释 - 那应该很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...explaining you. - That should prove interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点！看好路！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look out, will you? Why don't you watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要行窃吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Theft, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，我们先劫富，完事了…再济贫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we'll steal from the rich and give back to the poor later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉喜欢上了这个年代，单纯好应付\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'm gonna like this century. Simple, easier to manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们解释起来也不会太难…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not gonna have any difficulty explaining--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个警官，我认得老军装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a police officer. I recognise the traditional accoutrements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说会很好解释的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were saying you'll have no trouble explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我这朋友显然是个中国人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My friend is obviously Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你注意到他的耳朵了，其实是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see you've noticed the ears. They're actually easy to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是我在小时候遭遇的不幸意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps the unfortunate accident I had as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候遭遇的不幸意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The unfortunate accident he had as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他的头被卡在一台…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He caught his head in a mechanical...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,…碾米机里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...rice picker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，幸运的是附近有个美国传教士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, fortunately, there was an American missionary living close by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他的主业正好是整形医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who was actually a skilled plastic surgeon in civilian life--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，好吧！放下装束把手放在墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, all right! Drop those bundles and put your hands on that wall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你妻子太粗心了，让你穿成这样出门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, how careless of your wife to let you go out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 哦，是的，十分凌乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Oh, yes, it's quite untidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,过来，我帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上你喜欢我以前的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were actually enjoying my predicament back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 偶尔你看上去像人 - 舰长，作为我的长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- At times, you seem quite human. - Captain, I hardly believe that insults
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像无权这样侮辱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are within your prerogative as my commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到了困境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time we faced the unpleasant facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，我觉得我们比麦考伊早到一周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, I believe we have about a week before McCoy arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我们不确定 - 在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- but we can't be certain. - Arrives where,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,檀香山，博伊西，圣地亚哥？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Honolulu, Boise, San Diego?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不是外蒙古呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not Outer Mongolia, for that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,逻辑上讲时间是流动的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There could be some logic to the belief that time is fluid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一流河，有水流和漩涡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like a river with currents, eddies, backwash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有个漩涡把麦考伊带到某时某地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the same currents that swept McCoy to a certain time and place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或许也会把我们带到那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}might sweep us there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们只能希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless that is true, captain, we have no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,无法得知他到达的确切时间和地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Frustrating. Locked in here is the exact place and moment of his arrival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至想象他在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even the images of what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我能将传感器和星舰电脑连接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If only I could tie this tricorder in with the ship's computers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕就几分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for just a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你能在这制造一台电脑吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Couldn't you build some form of computer aid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个还在使用真空管的年代？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In this zinc-plated, vacuum-tubed culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，逻辑上讲它很复杂，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, well, it would pose an extremely complex problem in logic, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我有时候对你期望太高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me. I sometimes expect too much of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，小姐，我们冒昧打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse us, miss. We didn't mean to trespass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,外面很冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's cold outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,用谎言来打招呼很可怜，外面没那么冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lie is a very poor way to say hello. It isn't that cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正被警察追捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were being chased by a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就为这些衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,偷来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We stole them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没一点钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We didn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我可以帮你们一把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I could do with some help around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,洗盘子，扫地，日常打扫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}doing dishes, sweeping, general cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能给多少钱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At what rate of payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要真空电子管，我的爱好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need radio tubes and so forth. My hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,每小时15分，一天10小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fifteen cents an hour for ten hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们叫什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫寇克，他是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mine is Jim Kirk. His is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,…史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫伊迪丝·凯乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Edith Keeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，就从打扫这里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you can start by cleaning up down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在21街传教所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in the 21st Street Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你负责这里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you run this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，寇克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed I do, Mr. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,电子真空管之类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Radio tubes and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我欣赏爱好，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I approve of hobbies, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会后悔的 - 为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You'll be sorry. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上哪有免费午餐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You expect to eat for free or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你得听人说教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You gotta listen to goody two-shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我听到一些流言蜚语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now, as I'm sure that somebody out there has said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候付汤钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's time to pay for the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她长得倒算不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not that she's a bad-looking broad,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果她真的想帮助大伙摆脱困境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but if she really wanted to help out a fella in need--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shut up. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信她说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna hear what she has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，当然，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, of course, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们直说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, let's start by getting one thing straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是一个慈善家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not a do-gooder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你好吃懒做，还是个酒鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're a bum, if you can't break off with the booze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,或者其它任何坏习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or whatever it is that makes you a bad risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算告诉你们怎样寻找爱和幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I don't pretend to tell you how to find happiness and love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们尚未解决温饱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when every day is just a struggle to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我相信你们应该努力生存\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I do insist that you do survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为未来的生活将更美好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because the days and the years ahead are worth living for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不久的一天…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One day soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,…人类能够驾驭惊人的能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...man is going to be able to harness incredible energies...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,…甚至是原子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...maybe even the atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能把我们送到其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energies that could ultimately hurl us to other worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,通过某种宇宙飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in some sort of spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人类到达太空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the men that reach out into space
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有办法养活全世界千百万挨饿的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will be able to find ways to feed the hungry millions of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,治愈他们的疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and to cure their diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将能给每个人以希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They will be able to find a way to give each man hope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个正常的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and a common future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是活着的价值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And those are the days worth living for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠变绿洲…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our deserts will bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.85,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不久的将来发展原子能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Development of atomic power is years away,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,之后是太空飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}space flight years after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然，这些不会很快发生 - 天才的洞察力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Now, it won't happen tomorrow, - Speculation. Gifted insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但一定会实现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她很特别，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find her most uncommon, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为明天而打基础，作好准备不要放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prepare for tomorrow. Get ready. Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你真了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are uncommon workmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,地下室看上去抛过光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That basement looks like it's been scrubbed and polished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们汇报其他工作？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we can report back for other work?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，早上7点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, 7:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你晚上有地铺睡吗？ - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you have a flop for the night? - A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这方面你是个新人，不是吗？地铺就是睡觉的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You really are new at this, aren't you? A flop is a place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有间空房，2块钱一礼拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a vacant room at the place where I live for $2 a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你需要，我会带你过去 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- If you want to, I'll take you there. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有地铺了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a flop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们有啥？舰长 - 睡觉的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We have a what, captain? - A place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.34,0:24:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没人早点说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One might have said so in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我得要些铂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I must have some platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一小块就够了，5或者6磅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A small block would be sufficient, 5 or 6 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.72,0:25:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,通上电流之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By passing certain circuits through there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用作双励磁铁芯--\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be used as a duo-dynetic field core--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我给你买了些蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, I've brought you some assorted vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.64,0:25:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,腊肠和硬皮卷归我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bologna and a hard roll for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.52,0:25:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,花了过去3天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I've spent the other nine-tenths
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.07,0:25:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,工资总和的另外九成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of our combined salaries for the last three days
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来满足你的这些要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on filling this order for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.40,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，这个袋子里没有铂金或者金银\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, this bag does not contain platinum, silver or gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.78,0:25:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,短期之内我们也买不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nor is it likely to in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你要我对付的这些设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, you're asking me to work with equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是原始的石刀或兽皮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which is hardly very far ahead of stone knives and bearskins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊过几天就要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy will be along in a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也许更快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}perhaps sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.17,0:25:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能保证到时这些电路会把我们凑到一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no guarantee that these currents in time will bring us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 试了才知道 - 舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This has to work. - Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.81,0:25:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，按目前速度要三周甚至一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, in three weeks at this rate, possibly a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.89,0:25:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能在制造最早的存储电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might reach the first mnemonic memory circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.27,0:26:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在跟我走，有个5个小时的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you can leave right away, I can get you five hours work
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.90,0:26:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每小时22美分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at 22 cents an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.49,0:26:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？那究竟是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What--? What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.08,0:26:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人，我正试图构建初始存储电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am endeavouring, ma'am, to construct a mnemonic memory circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.88,0:26:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,用石刀和兽皮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}using stone knives and bearskins.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.12,0:26:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.04,0:27:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,干细活的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tools for finely detailed work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.68,0:27:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个盒子用密码锁锁着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That toolbox was locked with a combination lock,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.52,0:27:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你开的非常专业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you opened it like a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.52,0:27:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么那样做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.15,0:27:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要这些精美工具制作无线电设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I needed the fine tools for my radio work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天一亮我就还回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'd have been returned in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.70,0:27:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，对不起，我不能 - 如果史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, I'm sorry, I can't-- - If Mr. Spock
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.20,0:27:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说他需要这些工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}says that he needs the tools
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.87,0:27:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上得放回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that they'd be returned tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.33,0:27:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用声誉担保，凯乐小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you can bet your reputation on that, Miss Keeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.67,0:27:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有个条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.64,0:27:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我走回去？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Walk me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.18,0:27:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有几个问题正要问你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still have a few questions I'd like to ask about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.48,0:28:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摆出那种“又来审问我俩”的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and don't give me that "questions-about-little-old-us" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.77,0:28:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道你们俩和环境格格不入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know as well as I do how out of place you two are around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.07,0:28:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.95,0:28:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我们来自哪里，凯乐小姐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where would you estimate we belong, Miss Keeler?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.66,0:28:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,…站在他的立场，好像你一直在他身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...at his side, as if you've always been there and always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.37,0:28:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.58,0:28:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你来自其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You belong in another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.17,0:28:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道哪里，怎么来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know where or how.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要彻底弄明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll figure it out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要处理火炉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll finish with the furnace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.06,0:28:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“舰长”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.48,0:28:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他没开口，似乎都在说那个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even when he doesn't say it, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.29,0:29:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安，亲爱的，即使我不在你身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good night, sweetheart Though I'm not beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.38,0:29:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安，亲爱的，我的爱依旧向着你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good night, sweetheart Still my love will guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.13,0:29:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么史波克叫你舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why does Spock call you captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.97,0:29:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一起打过仗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Were you in the war together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.97,0:29:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起服役\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We served together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.14,0:29:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想讲讲？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you don't want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.02,0:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你做错了什么？你害怕什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you do something wrong? Are you afraid of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.82,0:29:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎么样我都会帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it is, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.78,0:29:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会帮你”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Let me help."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.95,0:29:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在之后一百年，我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A hundred years or so from now, I believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.25,0:29:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一位著名小说家会以此写出一部经典\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a famous novelist will write a classic using that theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.79,0:29:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他将推崇这三个字甚至超过“我爱你”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll recommend those three words even over "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.09,0:29:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,几个世纪后？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Centuries from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.17,0:29:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁？他是哪里人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who is he? Where does he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.22,0:29:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他会是哪里人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where will he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.68,0:29:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,天真的问题，想要天真的回答吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Silly question. Wanna hear a silly answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.01,0:30:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.89,0:30:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,猎户座腰带最左边的恒星，它的其中一颗行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A planet circling that far left star in Orion's belt. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.53,0:30:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,石刀和兽皮怎样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are the stone knives and bearskins?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.28,0:31:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概找到焦点了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I may have found our focal point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.53,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你也应该发现有个地方烧焦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you may also find you have a connection burning someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我使它们过载了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I'm overloading those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.41,0:31:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我们在这屏幕上找到答案了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe we'll have our answer on this screen, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.71,0:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 可是，舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Good. - And, captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.58,0:31:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- …你会发现这有些痛苦 - 好吧，让我看看你发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...you may find this a bit distressing. - Well, let's see what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.13,0:31:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我减慢了时间涡流中的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've slowed down the recording we made from the time vortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.09,0:31:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,1936年2月23日，从现在起六年后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}February 23, 1936. Six years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.07,0:31:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“总统和伊迪丝·凯乐…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"The president and Edith Keeler...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.24,0:31:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,…今天某时被授予”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...conferred for some time today--"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.71,0:31:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有多糟？ - 糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How bad? - Bad enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.47,0:32:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总统和伊迪丝·凯乐… - 看上去不太可能，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The president and Edith Keeler... - It would seem unlikely, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.39,0:32:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才，我看了1930年的报纸文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A few moments ago, I read a 1930 newspaper article.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.56,0:32:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道她的将来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know her future.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.35,0:32:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起6年内她将变的非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Within six years from now, she'll become very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.61,0:32:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 全国闻名 - 然而，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- nationally famous. - Or, captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪丝·凯乐会在这一年死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Edith Keeler will die this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.91,0:32:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到她的讣告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw her obituary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.96,0:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,某个交通意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some sort of traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.05,0:32:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.34,0:32:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,都不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They both can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.93,0:32:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，伊迪丝·凯乐是我们要找的焦点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, Edith Keeler is the focal point in time we've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.01,0:32:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们和麦考伊闯入的时间点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The point in time that both we and Dr. McCoy have been drawn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.35,0:32:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她有两种可能的将来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She has two possible futures then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.85,0:32:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,根据她的生死…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And depending on whether she lives or dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,…所有的历史都将被改写\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...all of history will be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.86,0:33:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而麦考伊… - 是随机因素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And McCoy... - Is the random element.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.33,0:33:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那他会做什么？杀了她？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In his condition, what does he do? Does he kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或他阻止她被杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or perhaps he prevents her from being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.33,0:33:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道是哪种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't know which.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.09,0:33:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,修好这东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get this thing fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.38,0:33:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须在麦考伊来之前弄清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must find out before McCoy arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，假设我们发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, suppose we discover
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.59,0:33:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让事情顺其自然的话，伊迪丝·凯乐必须死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that in order to set things straight again, Edith Keeler must die?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.51,0:34:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀！杀手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Assassins! Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.18,0:34:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,杀手！谋杀！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Murderers! Assassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.48,0:34:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,问你，这是什么星球？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You, what planet is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.87,0:34:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不要跑！我要杀了你！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! Don't run! I won't kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.99,0:34:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们杀了人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's they who do the killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.87,0:34:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跑！我要杀了你！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't run! I won't kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.84,0:35:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么人们对登上月球不屑一顾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why? What is so funny about man reaching for the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.59,0:35:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是怎么知道的？ - 我就是知道了，仅此而已，我能感觉到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How do you know? - I just know, that's all. I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.18,0:35:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，我觉得会有一天他们把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And more, I think that one day they're going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.56,0:35:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,花在战争和死亡上的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all the money that they spend now on war and death--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.39,0:35:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都用在拯救生命上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And make them spend it on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.02,0:35:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.78,0:35:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想法一致，语言相通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see the same things that I do. We speak the same language.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.54,0:35:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,非常一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The very same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.13,0:35:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你也逃出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad you got away too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊，我… - 为什么你觉得他们要杀我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yeah, I... - Why do you think they wanna kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.88,0:35:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看，小伙子，你喝多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, fella, you take a sip too much of that old wood alky,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.43,0:35:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去每件事都像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and almost anything seems like it--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.47,0:35:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.48,0:35:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,地球？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:36:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,星座看上去是的，可是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The constellations seem right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.61,0:36:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 解释这一切 - 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Explain this trick. - I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.91,0:36:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有两条腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.79,0:36:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,矮小的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Small.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.17,0:36:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,出色的颅骨进化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good cranial development.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.46,0:36:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是人类血统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No doubt considerable human ancestry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.84,0:36:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是如何伪装这些的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that how you're able to fake all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.47,0:36:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.39,0:36:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的现代博物馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Modern museum perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.39,0:36:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,混凝土柱子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right down to the cement beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.32,0:36:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,非常，非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.65,0:36:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我最好去医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'd give a lot to see the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.61,0:36:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大概要缝几针\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably needles and sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.41,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.83,0:37:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以前的医院把人当衣服切开再缝上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Used to had to cut and sew people like garments.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.09,0:37:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用针缝合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Needles and sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.01,0:37:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The terrible pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.36,0:38:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有多久得到完整的答案？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long before we get a full answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.08,0:38:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在我再次尝试前至少需要两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll need at least two more days before I dare make another attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.37,0:38:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,据我们所知麦考伊可能一周前就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy could have been in the city a week now for all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.88,0:38:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他的行为影响她或者改变历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And whatever he does that affects her and changes history
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.67,0:38:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可能就在今晚或明早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could happen tonight, tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.59,0:38:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.63,0:38:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们捕获的最后一点信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...our last bit of information was obtained
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.93,0:38:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是以30小时工作和烧掉电路为代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the expense of 30 hours' work in fused and burned circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.81,0:38:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须知道她是生是死，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must know whether she lives or dies, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.19,0:38:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须知道该做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,号外！号外！卖报纸啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Extra! Extra! Get your morning paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,买张报纸，看看啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get your paper. Read all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.68,0:39:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，小姐…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.31,0:39:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,…那咖啡，闻起来好香啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that coffee, it just smells wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.89,0:39:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你气色真难看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.94,0:39:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你最好坐下，来吧 - 不行，我必须一直走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You better sit down. Come on. - I can't. I gotta keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.15,0:39:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让他们找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't let them find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.03,0:39:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,后屋有张简易床，在那儿他们找不到你，来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a cot in the backroom. They won't find you there. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.05,0:39:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是麦考伊改变的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is how history went after McCoy changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.26,0:39:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，30年代后期崛起和平运动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, in the late 1 930s, a growing pacifist movement
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.68,0:40:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谁耽误了美国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whose influence delayed the United States' entry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.27,0:40:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,加入二战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}into the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.52,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,接着和平谈判被耽搁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While peace negotiations dragged on,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.02,0:40:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,德国就有时间完成重水实验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Germany had time to complete its heavy-water experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.52,0:40:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,德国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.15,0:40:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,法西斯，希特勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fascism, Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.40,0:40:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利万岁！胜利万岁！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sieg Heil! Sieg Heil!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.12,0:40:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,赢得二战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Won the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.87,0:40:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为所有这一切使他们率先发展原子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because all this lets them develop the A-bomb first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.96,0:40:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这没错，舰长，让我再来一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no mistake, captain. Let me run it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.80,0:40:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪丝·凯乐，和平运动创始人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Edith Keeler, founder of the peace movement."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.22,0:40:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她是对的，和平是条明路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But she was right, peace was the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.55,0:40:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她没错，但不是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was right, but at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.72,0:40:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,由于原子弹，和他们的V-2火箭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the A-bomb, and with their V-2 rockets to carry them,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.35,0:40:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 德国称霸整个世界 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Germany captured the world. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.40,0:40:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些都是因为麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all this because McCoy came back
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.23,0:40:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以某种方式让她死于街头意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and somehow kept her from dying in a street accident
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:41:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就如原先那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as she was meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.03,0:41:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须阻止他，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must stop him, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.17,0:41:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她是怎么死的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.83,0:41:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪一天？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.21,0:41:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能通过图像估计常规事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can estimate general happenings from these images,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.55,0:41:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不能追溯准确的时间和行动，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I can't trace down precise actions at exact moments, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.43,0:41:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.93,0:41:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.06,0:41:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,…我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.77,0:41:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…我爱上伊迪丝·凯乐了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I'm in love with Edith Keeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.61,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，伊迪丝·凯乐必须死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, Edith Keeler must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.33,0:42:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，你现在还没完全好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, now, come on. You're not ready to take on any tigers just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.29,0:42:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.05,0:42:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,往常我都会问，“我在哪？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most common question to ask would be, "Where am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.18,0:42:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不想问了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think I'll ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.81,0:42:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么呢？ - 唯一的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why not? - The only possible answer
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.81,0:42:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最终都会发现我是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would conclusively prove that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.36,0:42:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,…要么无意识或者神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...either unconscious or demented.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.70,0:42:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里看上去像大约1920或25年的地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This looks like old Earth around 1920 or '25.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.04,0:42:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不介意是30年代吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you care to try for '30?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.63,0:42:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是失去意识的神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am unconscious or demented.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.84,0:42:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个和你一样谈论地球的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a friend that talks about Earth the same way that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.30,0:42:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想见他吗？ - 我是外科大夫，不是精神病大夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Would you like to meet him? - I'm a surgeon, not a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伦纳德·麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am Leonard McCoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.57,0:43:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰进取号上的高级医务官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}senior medical officer aboard the USs Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.08,0:43:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是不相信你，只是这不像海军服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't mean to disbelieve you, but that's hardly a Navy uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.25,0:43:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对极了，对极了，亲爱的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's quite all right. That's quite all right, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.21,0:43:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,…因为我也不信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...because I don't believe in you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.42,0:43:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,休息会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.94,0:43:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Edith.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.45,0:43:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在跟踪我吗？先生 - 还是别有用心地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you following me, sir? - With ulterior motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.28,0:43:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这总满意了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would that please you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.33,0:43:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望意味着什么--\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hope it means what--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.46,0:44:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我真笨！这楼梯我走了上千次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stupid! I've been up and down those stairs a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.58,0:44:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你我可能已经摔破膝盖了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could have broken my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.82,0:44:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我无意偷听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I did not plan to eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.28,0:44:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你当然不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, of course you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.99,0:44:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不指出当她绊倒…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must point out that when she stumbled...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.33,0:44:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不抓住她她可能已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...she might have died right there had you not caught her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.00,0:44:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到时候，麦考伊不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not yet time. McCoy isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.59,0:44:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对事实不太确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not that sure of our facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.01,0:44:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道何时才是确切的时候？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's to say when the exact time will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.76,0:45:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,救她，响应你内心的号召\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Save her, do as your heart tells you to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.52,0:45:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然而数百万无辜的人将死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and millions will die who did not die before.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.11,0:45:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.37,0:45:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇，你看上去气色真好，大夫 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, you look just fine, doctor. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.87,0:45:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你可能想看晚报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you might like to see the evening paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.21,0:45:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不一定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.13,0:45:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信自己是因强心剂产生了幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I've convinced myself that this is all in a cordrazine hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.21,0:45:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我觉得你不是幻觉 - 这就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But I've decided you're not. - That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.38,0:45:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你不是，你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you're not, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.93,0:45:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.39,0:45:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当你出现时，看得出你需要朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you showed up here, you looked like you could use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.31,0:45:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我并不是怀疑这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.31,0:45:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪里，你是负责人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about this place, you run it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.15,0:45:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力经营\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I try to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.23,0:45:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 必须的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why? - It's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.78,0:45:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，至少对于我来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it was for me, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.41,0:46:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may have saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.78,0:46:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,通常很多人都会吃错药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lots of people drink from the wrong bottle sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.25,0:46:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会错到我这种程度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not as wrong as the bottle I drank from.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.08,0:46:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我表达感激之情，也许这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Allow me to show my gratitude. Perhaps there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以做些什么报答你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can do around here to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.22,0:46:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个待会谈，我要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can talk about that later. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.13,0:46:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友要带我去看克拉克·盖博的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My young man is taking me to a Clark Gable movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.55,0:46:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁的电影？ - 克拉克·盖博\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A who movie? - A Clark Gab--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.60,0:46:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难道你不知道？ - 好吧，我知道是什么电影，但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't you know? - Well, I know what a movie is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.77,0:46:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.69,0:46:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你休息会，回头见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You get some rest. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.63,0:47:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快点，我们能赶上奥芬剧院克拉克·盖博的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we hurry, maybe we can catch the Clark Gable movie at the Orpheum.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.47,0:47:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 我就是喜欢看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - I'd just love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.14,0:47:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗，麦考伊大夫也这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, Dr. McCoy said the same--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.89,0:47:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.06,0:47:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伦纳德·麦考伊？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leonard McCoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.52,0:47:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的，他有任务，他是 - 待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. He's in the mission. He's-- - Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.44,0:47:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！待在那里！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock! Stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.15,0:47:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么？ - 麦考伊，他就在…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is it? - McCoy, he's in--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.74,0:47:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老骨头！老骨头！ - 吉姆！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bones! Bones! - Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.16,0:47:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，吉姆！ - 伊迪丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, Jim! - Edith.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.56,0:47:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你故意阻止我的，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You deliberately stopped me, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.85,0:47:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以救她，你知道你刚才做了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could have saved her. Do you know what you just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.40,0:48:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道的，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He knows, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.53,0:48:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.38,0:48:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么，长官？你只是刚离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened, sir? You only left a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.51,0:48:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.69,0:48:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,时间继续流转，一切照旧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time has resumed its shape. All is as it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.07,0:48:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,许多这样的旅行是可行的，我的大门为你们敞开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Many such journeys are possible. Let me be your gateway.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.78,0:48:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，进取号已经就绪，他们问我们是否返回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the Enterprise is up there. They're asking if we wanna beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.38,0:48:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们离开这鬼地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get the hell out of here.
